{
  "stem": "8072.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we got there, and they didn't know where they-- he didn't know were the other people, there, sisters and brothers.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I said, let's go to my place-- I don't remember whether he give me addresses or not-- to where my sister is, and then we'll see if they can find.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So anyhow, to-- we got to my sister's, I ring the bell, or knock on the door, and somebody opens the door.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it wasn't my sister, because they happened to have-- there was a wedding going on that evening.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A girlfriend of theirs got married, and they had the biggest apartment, a two-bedroom apartment, so the wedding was in their house.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I said, whoever opened the door, I don't remember, and they say, yes, can I help you?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said, well, who is-- is-- I'm looking for Sabina or Helen Price.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Do-- they said, well, what are you-- who are you?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What are-- I said, I'm their brother.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she run in to get my sisters, you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my older sister fainted.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And my youngest-- and my brother was there, too.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And everybody, the whole family, was there, in the thing like that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So was it a nice reunion that time, you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And from there, where did you go?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From there, my sister said to me, you know, that when they survived-- when we gave a lot of belongings to the farmer that-- to that farmer, and to other farmers.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when my sister got back, she, she went to the farm, asking maybe they can give us something back, or help or something.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They said, we don't know you.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If your brother, or something-- like, my brother.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was the baby.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my brother was-- they were doing some business in the farm.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
